- title "The Demo"

/ Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action
.jumbotron.content-header.text-center
  .container
    %h1 DEMO
    %p your customers' experience - take a test drive
.container
  / Example row of columns
  .row
    .text-center.col-sm-3
      =image_tag "28.png", class: "img"
      %h2.lead the dokspot code
      %p.text-justify Each instruction is given a unique dokspot code, supplied with the product.
      %p.text-justify
        In this demo we use:
        %strong DKS16
      %p.text-justify Or scan this QR code (may also be supplied with the product) with your smartphone and jump to step 3.
      %hr.visible-xs-block.visible-sm-block
    .text-center.col-sm-3
      =image_tag "30.png", class: "img", style: "max-width: 200"
      %h3.lead view the product page
      %p.text-justify
        Now that you have a code, head over to
      %p.text-center
        %a{:href => "http://www.dokspot.com", :target => "_blank"} dokspot.com
      %p.text-justify and enter the code.
      %hr.visible-xs-block.visible-sm-block
    .text-center.col-sm-3
      =image_tag "23.png", class: "img"
      %h3.lead select a language
      %p.text-justify View all languages that the instruction has been made available as well as any important messages related to the product.
    .text-center.col-sm-3
      =image_tag "31.png", class: "img"
      %h3.lead view the instruction
      %p.text-justify Congratulation! You are now viewing your first document on the dokspot platform!
      %p.text-justify Simple enough? We think so. Click below to find out more about the service.
  .row{:style => "margin-top: 50px; margin-bottom: 50px"}
    .col-sm-3.text-center.hidden-xs
      %button.btn.btn-default.btn-primary{"data-target" => "#modalDemo1", "data-toggle" => "modal", :type => "button"} More Info
    .col-sm-3.text-center.hidden-xs
      %button.btn.btn-default.btn-primary{"data-target" => "#modalDemo2", "data-toggle" => "modal", :type => "button"} More Info
    .col-sm-3.text-center.hidden-xs
      %button.btn.btn-default.btn-primary{"data-target" => "#modalDemo3", "data-toggle" => "modal", :type => "button"} More Info
    .col-sm-3.text-center
      =link_to "The Service", service_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-success"  
      
/ /container
#modalDemo1.modal.fade.pg-show-modal{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1"}
  .modal-dialog
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        %button.close{"aria-hidden" => "true", "data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} ×
        %h4.modal-title the dokspot code
      .modal-body
        .row
          .col-md-6
            =image_tag "29.png", class: "img", width: 270
          .col-md-6
            %p.text-justify Customers receive a unique dokspot code with each product. For added customer convenience device manufacturers may also choose to supply a QR code. Both codes are automatically generated through the dokspot platform for further use by the device manufacturer.
            %p.text-justify Device manufacturers can choose from several dokspot templates for communication of the dokspot code, ranging from labels on consumable products, a permanent label on reusable devices or equipment or a product insert supplied with each product.
#modalDemo2.modal.fade.pg-show-modal{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1"}
  .modal-dialog
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        %button.close{"aria-hidden" => "true", "data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} ×
        %h4.modal-title view the product
      .modal-body
        .row
          .col-md-6
            =image_tag "32.png", class: "img", width: 270
          .col-md-6
            %p.text-justify With dokspot your customers get access to language tailored instructions quickly and securely. Our 2-step process is specifically designed for positive customer experience. If you customers want to read instructions they just enter the dokspot code in the dedicated platform or scan the QR code and select their language. 
            %p.text-justify dokspot service is accessible 24/7, thus allowing your customers access to instructions anytime and anywhere even without breaking the product seal.
#modalDemo3.modal.fade.pg-show-modal{"aria-hidden" => "true", :role => "dialog", :tabindex => "-1"}
  .modal-dialog
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        %button.close{"aria-hidden" => "true", "data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} ×
        %h4.modal-title select a language
      .modal-body
        .row
          .col-md-6
            =image_tag "33.png", class: "img", width: 270
          .col-md-6
            %p.text-justify Most instructions have a font size of 6 or smaller which is known to lead to slower reading pace and a reduced overall comprehension of the material. In addition customer receive instructions in many languages they don’t need, which is seen as cumbersome and wasteful.
            %p.text-justify dokspot improves your customers’ experience by providing language tailored instructions on a dedicated platform.